      "text": "NO Redis — every read = sqlc → MySQL.\nClient-side only: stats stale 30s/refetch 60s;\nexpanded stale 15s (lazy).\n🔴 status is WRITE-ONCE 'pending' — no UPDATE\nquery exists → 3/4 KPIs + quality permanently 0.",
      "fontSize": 10,
      "fontFamily": 3,
