      "frameId": null,
      "text": "CreateStaffTask     (INSERT 'pending')\nGetStaffTaskByID    (re-read)\nGetStaffTasksByDate (list)\nGetDailyTaskMetrics + GetStaffTaskStats\n\n✗ NO UpdateStaffTask\n✗ NO DeleteStaffTask\n✗ NO status-transition query\n\nfk_tasks_assigned_to → staff(id)\n  bad staffId ⇒ FK 1452 ⇒ 500 (Bug 3)",
      "fontSize": 11,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "CreateStaffTask     (INSERT 'pending')\nGetStaffTaskByID    (re-read)\nGetStaffTasksByDate (list)\nGetDailyTaskMetrics + GetStaffTaskStats\n\n✗ NO UpdateStaffTask\n✗ NO DeleteStaffTask\n✗ NO status-transition query\n\nfk_tasks_assigned_to → staff(id)\n  bad staffId ⇒ FK 1452 ⇒ 500 (Bug 3)",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
